# ── Proxmark3 GUI ───────────────────────────────────────────────

# Upstream Proxmark3 SOURCE tree: not needed to run the GUI (the GUI drives the
# bundled client in pm3gui/pm3client/), and it is very large.
# >> Delete the next line if you intentionally want the full source in the repo.
/proxmark3-master/

# Python bytecode / caches
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]

# Bundled-client runtime output written next to the exe (logs, prefs, history,
# temp). These must NOT be committed — but the client itself IS committed.
pm3gui/pm3client/.proxmark3/
pm3gui/pm3client/tmp/
**/.proxmark3/

# Logs
*.log

# Editor / tooling artifacts
.history
.history/
.vscode/
.idea/
.claude/

# OS cruft
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
desktop.ini
